@using Condominium2000.Helpers
@using Condominium2000.Helpers.Models
@using Condominium2000.Resources
@using Condominium2000.Resources.Resident
@using Condominium2000.Resources.Shared
@model Condominium2000.Models.ViewModels.ResidentViewModel

@{
    ViewBag.Title = Gallery.VIEW_BAG_TITLE;
}

<link href="@Url.Content("~/Content/ImageSliderDefault/js-image-slider-default.css")" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
<script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/ImageSliderDefault/js-image-slider-default.js")" type="text/javascript"></script>

<div id="content_margin_top"></div>
<div id="content_center" class="center">
    <div id="content_top">
        <div id="content_margin_left"></div>
        <div id="content_small">
            <div id="sidebar_menu" class="sidebar_menu">
                @Html.Partial("_SubMenuPartial", ResidentHelper.SubMenu.Gallery)
                <div class="sidebar_menu_divider"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="content_margin_middle"></div>
        <div id="content_large">
            <div class="sidebar_margin_xl"></div>
            @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
            {
                <div class="edit_link">
                    <p>
                        [@Html.ActionLink(EditLabels.LABEL_ADMIN_GALLERY_IMAGES, "AdminGalleryImages", new {controller = "GalleryImage"})]
                    </p>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <br/>
            }

            <div id="sliderFrame">
                <div id="ribbon"></div>
                <div id="slider">
                    @foreach (var image in Model.AllGalleryImages)
                    {
                        <a href="@image.FilePath">
                            <img src="@image.FilePath" alt="@Html.ReturnLanguageContent(image, TableContent.Caption)"/>
                        </a>
                    }
                </div>
                <div id="htmlcaption" style="display: none;">
                    <em>HTML</em> caption. Back to <a href="http://www.menucool.com/">Menucool</a>.
                </div>

                <!--thumbnails-->
                <div id="thumbs">
                    @foreach (var image in Model.AllGalleryImages)
                    {
                        <div class="thumb">
                            <img src="@image.FilePath" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="content_bottom" class="side_border">
        <div id="bottom_fast_links" class="quick_navigation">
            <div id="fl_divider">
                <div class="fl_divider"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="fl_space">
            </div>
            <div id="fl_news">
                @Html.ActionLinkBack(ContentBottom.BACK)
            </div>
            <div id="fl_top">
                @Html.ActionLinkTop(ContentBottom.TOP)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>